[22/02/2018 01:39:21] <font color="#0000ff">tiro un blincu del xergón</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:29] <font color="#0000ff">y voi a coller les berces</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:29] <font color="#0000ff">pa echar con fabes y con llacón</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:33] <font color="#0000ff">Si una vez o dos o tres,</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:37] <font color="#0000ff">baxo a la villa al mercáu</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:46] <font color="#0000ff">todos me miren de lláu</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:46] <font color="#0000ff">y dicen neña qué guapa yes</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:48] <font color="#ffffff">Porqué...</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:51] <font color="#0000ff">Ritmo...</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:53] <font color="#0000ff">Ritmo de Verdiciu...</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:55] <font color="#0000ff">Bellísima...</font>
[22/02/2018 01:39:58] <font color="#0000ff">Ritmo...</font>
[22/02/2018 01:40:01] <font color="#0000ff">Ritmo de Verdiciu...</font>
[22/02/2018 01:40:11] <font color="#0000ff">Tengo un mozacu, que me cortexa</font>
